    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. Mechanically, it runs smoothly with no known issues, and all major systems are functioning as they should. The interior is clean and smoke-free, though you might find some light wear on the driver's seat and floor mats. Externally, the paint retains a nice shine, with only a few minor stone chips and small scratches consistent with careful daily use. It is a dependable car that is ready for its next owner with no immediate repairs needed.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
