      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is mechanically flawless, boasting a comprehensive service history including proactive rod bearing replacement and a full VANOS overhaul. The chassis integrity is guaranteed with documented subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein dampers. Power is transferred via a precise 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential. Finished in Alpine White with a pristine interior, this collector-grade unit exhibits zero deferred maintenance and perfect compression across all cylinders.",
